#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.38"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.38:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.38:0.2"
msgid "4. Sumanavagga"
msgstr "4. With Sumanā"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.38:0.3"
msgid "38. Saddhasutta"
msgstr "38. Faith"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.38:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, saddhe kulaputte ānisaṃsā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, a faithful person from a good family gets five benefits."

msgctxt "an5.38:1.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.38:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye te, bhikkhave, loke santo sappurisā te saddhaññeva paṭhamaṃ anukampantā "
"anukampanti, no tathā assaddhaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The good persons in the world show compassion first to the faithful, not so "
"much to the unfaithful."

msgctxt "an5.38:1.4"
msgid "saddhaññeva paṭhamaṃ upasaṅkamantā upasaṅkamanti, no tathā assaddhaṃ;"
msgstr "They first approach the faithful, not so much the unfaithful."

msgctxt "an5.38:1.5"
msgid "saddhaññeva paṭhamaṃ paṭiggaṇhantā paṭiggaṇhanti, no tathā assaddhaṃ;"
msgstr "They first receive alms from the faithful, not so much the unfaithful."

msgctxt "an5.38:1.6"
msgid "saddhaññeva paṭhamaṃ dhammaṃ desentā desenti, no tathā assaddhaṃ;"
msgstr "They first teach Dhamma to the faithful, not so much the unfaithful."

msgctxt "an5.38:1.7"
msgid "saddho kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, the faithful are reborn in a good "
"place, a heavenly realm."

msgctxt "an5.38:1.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca saddhe kulaputte ānisaṃsā."
msgstr "A faithful person from a good family gets these five benefits."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.43"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.38:2.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, subhūmiyaṃ catumahāpathe mahānigrodho samantā "
"pakkhīnaṃ paṭisaraṇaṃ hoti;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a great banyan tree at a level crossroads. It would become "
"a refuge for birds from all around."

msgctxt "an5.38:2.2"
msgid ""
"evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, saddho kulaputto bahuno janassa paṭisaraṇaṃ hoti "
"bhikkhūnaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ upāsakānaṃ upāsikānanti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a faithful person from a good family becomes a refuge for "
"many people—monks, nuns, laywomen, and laymen."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: Sākhāpattaphalūpeto → sākhāpattaphalupeto (pts1) | sākhāpattabahupeto (katthaci) | sākhāpattapalāsūpeto (?)
msgctxt "an5.38:3.1"
msgid "Sākhāpattaphalūpeto,"
msgstr "With its branches, leaves, and fruit,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: khandhimāva → khandhimā ca (bj)
msgctxt "an5.38:3.2"
msgid "khandhimāva mahādumo;"
msgstr "a great tree with its strong trunk,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:3.3"
msgid "Mūlavā phalasampanno,"
msgstr "firmly-rooted and fruit-bearing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:3.4"
msgid "patiṭṭhā hoti pakkhinaṃ."
msgstr "supports many birds."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.38:4.1"
msgid "Manorame āyatane,"
msgstr "It’s a lovely place,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:4.2"
msgid "sevanti naṃ vihaṅgamā;"
msgstr "frequented by the sky-soarers."

#. <br>
#. VAR: chāyatthikā → chāyatthino (si)
msgctxt "an5.38:4.3"
msgid "Chāyaṃ chāyatthikā yanti,"
msgstr "Those that need shade go in the shade,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:4.4"
msgid "phalatthā phalabhojino."
msgstr "those that need fruit enjoy the fruit."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.38:5.1"
msgid "Tatheva sīlasampannaṃ,"
msgstr "So too, a faithful individual"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:5.2"
msgid "saddhaṃ purisapuggalaṃ;"
msgstr "is perfect in ethics,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:5.3"
msgid "Nivātavuttiṃ atthaddhaṃ,"
msgstr "humble and kind,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:5.4"
msgid "sorataṃ sakhilaṃ muduṃ."
msgstr "sweet, friendly, and tender."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.38:6.1"
msgid "Vītarāgā vītadosā,"
msgstr "Those free of greed, freed of hate,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:6.2"
msgid "vītamohā anāsavā;"
msgstr "free of delusion, undefiled,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:6.3"
msgid "Puññakkhettāni lokasmiṃ,"
msgstr "fields of merit for the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:6.4"
msgid "sevanti tādisaṃ naraṃ."
msgstr "associate with such a person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.38:7.1"
msgid "Te tassa dhammaṃ desenti,"
msgstr "They teach them the Dhamma,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:7.2"
msgid "Sabbadukkhāpanūdanaṃ;"
msgstr "that dispels all suffering."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:7.3"
msgid "Yaṃ so dhammaṃ idhaññāya,"
msgstr "Understanding this teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.38:7.4"
msgid "Parinibbāti anāsavo”ti."
msgstr "they’re extinguished without defilements.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.38:7.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
